#. S01 intro
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/scenarios/01_Pirates.cfg:26
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Far north from Westin, on the west coast of the kingdom, there lies a "
#| "place called the Bay of Pearls. The waters of the bay are calm, and "
#| "clear, and warm even in winter. But its most notable feature is that for "
#| "which it is named — abundant beds of oysters and a vast wealth in pearls."
msgid ""
"Far north from Westin, on the west coast of the Kingdom of Wesnoth, there "
"lies a place called the Bay of Pearls. The waters of the bay are calm, and "
"clear, and warm even in winter. But its most notable feature is that for "
"which it is named — abundant beds of oysters and a vast wealth in pearls."
msgstr ""
"Muy al norte de Westin y al oeste de Aldril se encuentra un lugar llamado la "
"Bahía de las Perlas. Las aguas de la bahía son tranquilas, claras y "
"templadas incluso en invierno. Pero su rasgo más destacable es aquello por "
"lo que recibe su nombre: abundantes bancos de ostras y una inmensa riqueza "
"en perlas."

#. [part]
#. S01 intro
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/scenarios/01_Pirates.cfg:31
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Many have tried to claim the bay for their own; sometimes with words, and "
#| "sometimes with swords. But in the end the crown declared it the domain of "
#| "the merfolk, those most suited to care for and harvest the bay’s undersea "
#| "resources."
msgid ""
"Many have tried to claim the bay for their own; sometimes with words, and "
"sometimes with swords. But in the end the Crown declared it the domain of "
"the merfolk, those most suited to care for and harvest the bay’s undersea "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"Muchos han intentado apropiarse de la bahía, a veces con palabras y a veces "
"con espadas. Pero al final la corona la declaró dominio de los sirénidos, "
"los más capacitados para cuidar y cosechar los recursos submarinos de la "
"bahía."

#. [part]
