msgstr "Luchar en desventaja"

#. [display_tip]
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/scenarios/01_Pirates.cfg:293
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Your enemy in this scenario starts with much more gold than you.\n"
#| "Even worse, your only recruit options are Peasants and Woodsmen:\n"
#| "cheap-but-frail fighters with makeshift weapons and minimial \n"
#| "training. Peasants and Woodsmen are level 0 units, and as such \n"
#| "do not enforce a Zone of Control (enemies can move freely around \n"
#| "them without being stopped).\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Fortunately, you’re much smarter than our AI (probably), and this \n"
#| "scenario has a generous turn limit. Don’t sacrifice your entire \n"
#| "army right away. Play smart — control villages to gain gold and \n"
#| "use the time of day to your advantage. <i><b>Slowly build up your army\n"
#| "while whittling down the opponent’s.</b></i>"
msgid ""
"Your enemy in this scenario starts with much more gold than you.\n"
"Even worse, your only recruit options are Peasants and Woodsmen:\n"
"cheap-but-frail fighters with makeshift weapons and minimal \n"
"training. Peasants and Woodsmen are level 0 units, and as such \n"
"do not enforce a Zone of Control (enemies can move freely around \n"
"them without being stopped).\n"
"\n"
"Fortunately, you’re much smarter than our AI (probably), and this \n"
"scenario has a generous turn limit. Don’t sacrifice your entire \n"
"army right away. Play smart — control villages to gain gold and \n"
"use the time of day to your advantage. <i><b>Slowly build up your army\n"
"while whittling down the opponent’s.</b></i>"
msgstr ""
"En este escenario tu enemigo comienza con mucho más oro que tú.\n"
"Peor aún, tus únicas opciones de reclutamiento son campesinos y leñadores:\n"
"combatientes baratos pero frágiles, con armas improvisadas y entrenamiento "
"mínimo. Los campesinos y leñadores son unidades de nivel 0 y, por tanto, no "
"ejercen zona de control (los enemigos pueden moverse libremente a su "
"alrededor sin ser detenidos).\n"
"\n"
"Afortunadamente, eres mucho más listo que nuestra IA (probablemente) y este "
"escenario tiene un límite de turnos generoso. No sacrifiques todo tu "
"ejército de inmediato. Juega con inteligencia: controla aldeas para ganar "
"oro y aprovecha la hora del día a tu favor. <i><b>Construye poco a poco tu "
"ejército mientras desgastas al rival.</b></i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyn
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/scenarios/01_Pirates.cfg:308
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We’ll need more experienced fighters, too. You’ve done your best to train "
#| "me and Thea, pa, but most of the farmers are just that... farmers."
msgid ""
"We’ll need more experienced fighters, too. You’ve done your best to train me "
"and Thea, Pa, but most of the farmers are just that... farmers."
msgstr ""
"También necesitaremos combatientes más experimentados. Has hecho lo que has "
"podido para entrenar a Thea y a mí, pa, pero la mayoría de los granjeros son "
"solo eso… granjeros."

